title: DemoLab experiment with tabular data
body:
Motivation

Please summarize the aim of the experiment (1-2 lines).

Preparation

Please answer the preparation questions in the experiment instructions here. Bullet points, sketches and/or formulas are sufficient. Images can be inserted via copy/paste. Formulas can be entered using LaTeX code, e.g. 

$$R=\frac{U}{I}$$

results in: $$R=\frac{U}{I}$$

Experiment description

Describe the experiment here (e.g. circuit diagrams, experimental protocols, expected results). You may add further details to this section during the experiment (e.g. foto of the setup).

Results

Note your experimental results here, i.e. observations and manually collected data. Insert the latter into the following table (tabular data can be read via Python for data evaluation). You can also add further tables for additional measurement series.

quantity1 (unit) quantity2 (unit)
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   
   

Evaluation

Makes notes here on how you evaluated the data. Also report your results.
